WEBVTT

00:00:00.205 --> 00:00:02.132
[Production supported by the
Ministry of Culture, Sports and Tourism]

00:00:02.151 --> 00:00:03.152
[This drama is fictional.]

00:00:03.171 --> 00:00:04.066
[Child and animal scenes complied
with broadcast guidelines.]

00:00:04.171 --> 00:00:06.757
It's You's mixed reality dating AI,

00:00:06.840 --> 00:00:07.840
is now revealed.

00:00:08.006 --> 00:00:10.335
This is the lowest quality
counterfeit among them all.

00:00:10.360 --> 00:00:12.111
I'm just worried about getting caught.

00:00:12.112 --> 00:00:14.509
"Exclusive! It's You's CEO Yun Bia."

00:00:14.534 --> 00:00:16.545
"Collapses after
spending an hour with people."

00:00:16.770 --> 00:00:19.080
What will happen to me now?

00:00:19.424 --> 00:00:20.833
You didn't collapse.

00:00:20.834 --> 00:00:23.568
Do you think it's related to
that writer Han Sunho?

00:00:23.635 --> 00:00:25.830
"Yun Bia and Han Sunho
caught holding hands."

00:00:25.831 --> 00:00:27.130
"A love escape"?

00:00:27.155 --> 00:00:28.794
You fight fire with fire.

00:00:28.795 --> 00:00:31.270
Then why did CEO Yun Bia
admit to the romance?

00:00:31.295 --> 00:00:33.074
Go ask that woman again.

00:00:33.075 --> 00:00:36.570
Writer Han Sunho is doing much better
than most celebrities.

00:00:36.785 --> 00:00:39.120
This is a sign Yun Bia's getting serious.

00:00:39.139 --> 00:00:40.939
What is this woman really thinking?

00:00:40.940 --> 00:00:42.884
She's probably thinking of
eating you alive.

00:00:43.470 --> 00:00:44.984
What if he finds out about your secret?

00:00:44.985 --> 00:00:46.615
I just need to gain the upper hand.

00:00:46.665 --> 00:00:47.653
Are you crazy?

00:00:48.056 --> 00:00:50.111
Is the company really closing down?

00:00:50.260 --> 00:00:51.121
Step aside.

00:00:51.277 --> 00:00:52.444
Let go of that hand.

00:00:52.445 --> 00:00:53.660
That's mine.

00:00:54.035 --> 00:00:54.980
Starting tomorrow,

00:00:55.067 --> 00:00:56.914
you can come to work at 'It's You'.

00:00:57.138 --> 00:00:59.898
I should at least know
what you're trying to do, right?

00:01:00.255 --> 00:01:04.782
Our goal is to gather information about
Writer Han without getting caught.

00:01:04.859 --> 00:01:07.432
What's she planning to do
with my portrait rights?

00:01:07.575 --> 00:01:11.086
From 'It's You', here's your
first look at the 'ForMe Version 2'.

00:01:11.105 --> 00:01:12.105
Meet Han Sunho.

00:01:12.175 --> 00:01:14.810
It seems someone tried to
breach the company's firewall.

00:01:15.031 --> 00:01:16.936
Yun Bia, look at me!

00:01:17.509 --> 00:01:20.459
Did you always have
this much interest in me?

00:01:20.460 --> 00:01:22.013
I do now.

00:01:22.400 --> 00:01:25.540
I’m okay when I’m with you, Han Sunho.

00:01:25.965 --> 00:01:27.532
Don't pin your hopes
on coincidence.

00:01:27.605 --> 00:01:28.814
It's not like you.

00:01:29.255 --> 00:01:31.627
You don’t have to come to work anymore.

00:01:31.646 --> 00:01:33.211
Did Yun Bia agree to this too?

00:01:33.330 --> 00:01:35.060
Yang Seonae has gone missing.

00:01:37.585 --> 00:01:40.900
You may make a good copy,
but it doesn't bring Mina back.

00:01:42.326 --> 00:01:43.028
Let’s go.

00:01:43.048 --> 00:01:44.048
Out into the world.

00:01:44.355 --> 00:01:45.810
You don’t have to do this.

00:01:45.885 --> 00:01:47.410
You're leaving now anyway.

00:01:47.737 --> 00:01:49.763
You brought me in on your terms,

00:01:49.831 --> 00:01:52.019
but it won't be like that
when I'm leaving.

00:01:52.161 --> 00:01:52.797
Where are you going?

00:01:52.829 --> 00:01:53.550
Where are you going?

00:01:53.647 --> 00:01:54.647
Where are you going?

00:01:54.735 --> 00:01:56.280
Ah, lucky you, Yun Bia.

00:01:56.455 --> 00:01:58.506
Do I look easy
now that you know my weakness?

00:01:58.691 --> 00:02:00.726
You’re harder for me than anything.

00:02:00.801 --> 00:02:02.826
Yun Bia, can I be there for you?

00:02:03.261 --> 00:02:04.261
Will you allow me?

00:02:04.641 --> 00:02:06.526
Does she like you back?

00:02:06.720 --> 00:02:09.884
Even if you get hurt again,
would you still be okay?

00:02:10.009 --> 00:02:11.592
It’s a package for you.

00:02:11.917 --> 00:02:13.612
Perhaps it's a message?

00:02:13.907 --> 00:02:15.532
It doesn’t just feel like a prank.

00:02:15.800 --> 00:02:17.721
Come out, I said come out!

00:02:18.146 --> 00:02:20.520
We need to remove anything
that gets in the way.

00:02:21.535 --> 00:02:22.885
You'll regret it.

00:02:23.310 --> 00:02:26.584
"If you don't want to die,
stay away from Yun Bia."

00:02:27.202 --> 00:02:28.770
Even if the whole
world turns against you,

00:02:28.846 --> 00:02:29.894
I'll be by your side.

00:02:30.409 --> 00:02:31.409
Aunt.

00:02:32.450 --> 00:02:33.450
There you are.

00:02:33.880 --> 00:02:34.713
My daughter.

00:02:35.020 --> 00:02:36.020
Mom...

00:02:37.021 --> 00:02:38.740
You said I could get better, right?

00:02:39.172 --> 00:02:40.577
You're wrong.

00:02:40.680 --> 00:02:42.075
Stay away from Bia.

00:02:42.334 --> 00:02:44.299
I will make Bia happy.

00:02:44.870 --> 00:02:46.101
Don't lie to yourself.

00:02:46.120 --> 00:02:50.028
We're the ones who want to be happy
by staying by her side.

00:02:50.166 --> 00:02:51.448
You know Yang Seonae, right?

00:02:51.482 --> 00:02:53.017
She's currently missing.

00:02:53.445 --> 00:02:55.945
There are other things
that bother me besides you.

00:02:56.070 --> 00:03:00.145
Detective, I'll send you an address,
so please head there now.

00:03:00.505 --> 00:03:03.629
It might be the place
where Yang Seonae is.

00:03:30.141 --> 00:03:33.685
Happy birthday to you.

00:03:33.855 --> 00:03:38.289
Dear teacher.

00:03:38.327 --> 00:03:41.590
Happy birthday to you.

00:03:41.610 --> 00:03:42.987
Woo!

00:03:43.007 --> 00:03:44.489
- Make a wish and blow out the candles.
- Thank you.

00:03:47.218 --> 00:03:48.840
Back to that day.

00:03:54.406 --> 00:03:56.454
As someone who
no longer exists in this world.

00:04:03.179 --> 00:04:04.102
You must return.

00:04:21.740 --> 00:04:22.955
Who are you?

00:04:28.812 --> 00:04:29.812
You are...

00:04:30.927 --> 00:04:32.740
Dad, if you meet this woman again,

00:04:34.673 --> 00:04:36.262
I'll kill her.

00:04:43.646 --> 00:04:45.126
Where do you think you're running to?

00:05:40.517 --> 00:05:43.001
Now you're trying to
take Bia away from me too?

00:05:43.963 --> 00:05:45.326
Not this time.

00:06:45.754 --> 00:06:47.419
Aunt, please wake up!

00:06:47.775 --> 00:06:49.032
Aunt Seonae!

00:06:49.757 --> 00:06:50.822
It's Sunho.

00:06:51.535 --> 00:06:53.020
Aunt, please wake up!

00:06:53.779 --> 00:06:54.779
Bia...

00:06:56.694 --> 00:06:58.069
My Bia...

00:07:04.310 --> 00:07:06.697
Even if a collision is expected

00:07:07.847 --> 00:07:09.743
there are times when
you don't realize.

00:07:13.098 --> 00:07:14.331
Whether by chance.

00:07:17.070 --> 00:07:18.269
Or intentional.

00:07:22.332 --> 00:07:23.778
There's no way to avoid it.

00:07:32.908 --> 00:07:34.199
I'll just go in for a moment.

00:07:34.321 --> 00:07:37.969
- I'll just go in for a moment.
- I'll just go in for a bit.

00:07:38.036 --> 00:07:39.889
You can't be doing this here.

00:07:41.413 --> 00:07:43.975
- Is Director Yun here?
- Director Yun is not here.

00:08:28.218 --> 00:08:29.726
You still have a fever...

00:08:39.535 --> 00:08:41.388
I know your heart is troubled too,

00:08:42.513 --> 00:08:44.843
But why don't you take care of yourself?

00:08:45.708 --> 00:08:47.343
I don't have the luxury for that.

00:08:48.603 --> 00:08:50.592
Company and everyone

00:08:50.881 --> 00:08:52.587
are falling apart.

00:08:53.049 --> 00:08:54.589
I can't just be comfortable.

00:08:55.595 --> 00:08:56.905
You can leave now.

00:08:58.798 --> 00:09:00.158
I want to be alone.

00:09:01.835 --> 00:09:04.450
If you feel like you're going to collapse,
lean on me.

00:09:05.058 --> 00:09:07.003
I told you I'd be by your side.

00:09:35.894 --> 00:09:36.999
[Yeon Woo]

00:09:37.018 --> 00:09:38.229
[Kim Hyun Jin]

00:09:44.455 --> 00:09:45.607
[Cho Yun Seo]

00:09:45.627 --> 00:09:46.791
[Choi Byung Chan]

00:09:49.294 --> 00:09:51.582
[Im Ji Eun]

00:10:00.436 --> 00:10:03.181
LOVE PHOBIA

00:10:03.414 --> 00:10:07.863
The rising AI company 'It's You'
faces its worst crisis.

00:10:07.864 --> 00:10:12.412
The hit-and-run incident involving
Yun Bia's mother, the late Yang Seonae.

00:10:12.413 --> 00:10:17.021
The prime suspect, Sul Jaehee,
is currently on the run.

00:10:17.041 --> 00:10:19.864
Users and investors
are angrily protesting

00:10:19.884 --> 00:10:25.343
for the suspension of It's You's
services and accountability.

00:10:25.436 --> 00:10:29.193
'It's You' must
immediately suspend services!

00:10:29.213 --> 00:10:31.102
Suspend! Suspend!

00:10:31.122 --> 00:10:34.291
Director Yun Bia must step down
from the company immediately!

00:10:34.311 --> 00:10:36.093
Step down! Step down!

00:10:36.113 --> 00:10:37.148
Director Yun! Director Yun!

00:10:37.168 --> 00:10:38.529
Hey, block Director Yun's car!

00:10:39.217 --> 00:10:40.592
Why are you here?

00:10:41.253 --> 00:10:42.253
Get out of the car!

00:10:42.508 --> 00:10:43.508
Get out of the car!

00:10:53.667 --> 00:10:56.074
Director Yun!
Why did Director Sul harm your mother?

00:10:56.075 --> 00:10:57.468
Was there a conflict between you two?

00:10:57.488 --> 00:10:59.096
Do you have a solution for this situation?

00:10:59.115 --> 00:11:00.320
Give me back my investment!

00:11:00.378 --> 00:11:02.080
What are we supposed to do now?

00:11:04.527 --> 00:11:05.527
Just a moment.

00:11:11.805 --> 00:11:14.725
Director Yun, is it true that a vote on
your dismissal is scheduled for today?

00:11:14.735 --> 00:11:16.735
Do you have any intention
of resigning voluntarily?

00:11:18.964 --> 00:11:20.244
Say something!

00:11:20.245 --> 00:11:21.480
Speak up!

00:11:21.481 --> 00:11:22.784
Director Yun, please say something.

00:11:22.785 --> 00:11:24.510
How are you going to resolve this?

00:11:33.020 --> 00:11:34.020
First,

00:11:35.281 --> 00:11:37.002
To everyone who
experienced discomfort

00:11:37.795 --> 00:11:40.630
and confusion due
to this series of events.

00:11:41.705 --> 00:11:43.460
I sincerely apologize.

00:11:44.215 --> 00:11:45.942
And for more details,

00:11:46.867 --> 00:11:49.920
I will address them in
an official press conference.

00:11:53.354 --> 00:11:55.195
What nonsense are you talking about?

00:11:58.095 --> 00:12:00.650
Do you know the total losses
of the shareholders?

00:12:01.065 --> 00:12:03.614
Propose the dismissal
of the Director immediately.

00:12:03.705 --> 00:12:06.891
Otherwise,
we will vote on the dismissal right here.

00:12:06.916 --> 00:12:09.245
The result is obvious.

00:12:09.246 --> 00:12:12.842
What can someone who was
always behind Director Sul do alone?

00:12:12.861 --> 00:12:15.365
Director Yun,
thank you for your hard work.

00:12:16.167 --> 00:12:20.596
By the way, who will compensate for
the losses left by 'It's You'?

00:12:20.615 --> 00:12:21.804
Yes, Director Yun should compensate.

00:12:21.805 --> 00:12:24.452
- Is there a plan for this now?
- Director Yun should take responsibility.

00:12:24.453 --> 00:12:25.999
I, Yun Bia,

00:12:27.403 --> 00:12:28.469
as of today

00:12:29.995 --> 00:12:32.116
will step down as the Director.

00:12:38.948 --> 00:12:41.759
To those who suffered due to 'It's You',

00:12:41.983 --> 00:12:46.590
I will find the best compensation
and solutions within my capabilities.

00:12:47.401 --> 00:12:50.528
Thank you for everything.

00:12:54.595 --> 00:12:58.360
How could Director Sul harm
Director Yun's mother...

00:12:59.130 --> 00:13:01.625
Losing her mother must be
hard enough for Director Yun,

00:13:01.844 --> 00:13:03.374
and now her friend and company too...

00:13:03.676 --> 00:13:05.696
What on earth happened?

00:13:06.935 --> 00:13:11.110
Think of all the time and effort you
dedicated to 'It's You'.

00:13:12.941 --> 00:13:13.691
Director Yun.

00:13:18.551 --> 00:13:19.670
I'm...

00:13:20.980 --> 00:13:22.266
not the Director anymore.

00:13:23.388 --> 00:13:25.503
Are you just leaving like this?

00:13:27.871 --> 00:13:29.674
My role ends here.

00:13:31.395 --> 00:13:32.522
For all this time,

00:13:33.647 --> 00:13:35.419
Thank you for following me,

00:13:36.679 --> 00:13:38.195
despite my shortcomings.

00:13:39.802 --> 00:13:40.998
I was grateful to you all.

00:13:49.889 --> 00:13:51.203
Director Yun!

00:13:55.138 --> 00:13:57.909
'It's You' isn't 'It's You'
without you, Director.

00:13:57.929 --> 00:14:00.264
We will continue to stand by you.

00:14:00.675 --> 00:14:01.675
Me too.

00:14:02.995 --> 00:14:04.460
Director Yun...

00:14:09.283 --> 00:14:10.434
Mr. Han!

00:14:10.873 --> 00:14:11.887
Mr. Han!

00:14:12.012 --> 00:14:13.020
Sir!

00:14:13.745 --> 00:14:15.084
Why are you hugging me?

00:14:15.085 --> 00:14:16.440
I love you, Mr. Han. No, I like you.

00:14:16.460 --> 00:14:17.473
I love you too, Mr. Han.

00:14:17.609 --> 00:14:18.660
Let go of me!

00:14:19.035 --> 00:14:21.761
- San, San, let go quickly.
- No, please, at 'It's You'...

00:14:21.762 --> 00:14:23.060
Let go of me, please!

00:14:28.060 --> 00:14:29.955
The staff also seemed
to really like you, Bia.

00:14:30.280 --> 00:14:33.290
I mean, Director Yun.

00:14:33.885 --> 00:14:35.142
Even if they couldn't say it.

00:14:35.748 --> 00:14:37.768
I should have treated
the staff better sooner.

00:14:38.565 --> 00:14:39.871
If I had known

00:14:40.280 --> 00:14:42.470
that being loved felt this good.

00:14:55.673 --> 00:14:56.622
I'll talk with Jaehee

00:14:57.692 --> 00:14:58.902
alone.

00:15:26.254 --> 00:15:28.219
Didn't you come because you had
something to say to me?

00:15:33.485 --> 00:15:35.412
What do you want to hear from me?

00:15:37.449 --> 00:15:39.630
Do you want me to
curse at you or something?

00:15:41.047 --> 00:15:42.113
I want to know...

00:15:43.352 --> 00:15:45.207
why you went that far.

00:15:46.932 --> 00:15:47.990
Why?

00:15:59.948 --> 00:16:01.719
Because losing my dad

00:16:02.679 --> 00:16:04.509
was because of your mom.

00:16:07.455 --> 00:16:09.673
That woman doesn't
deserve to be called a mom.

00:16:10.841 --> 00:16:12.882
Your mom ruined everything.

00:16:13.725 --> 00:16:16.870
My dad, your dad, you, and me!

00:16:20.355 --> 00:16:22.020
That's why I wanted to kill your mom.

00:16:26.311 --> 00:16:27.386
So,

00:16:29.485 --> 00:16:30.920
do you feel relieved now?

00:16:37.048 --> 00:16:39.723
I did it all for you, okay?

00:16:39.984 --> 00:16:44.080
Because when I'm by your side,
we're both happy.

00:16:44.375 --> 00:16:45.080
So...

00:16:45.080 --> 00:16:46.080
Well...

00:16:47.676 --> 00:16:49.213
I also believed

00:16:50.229 --> 00:16:52.797
you were the only family I had left.

00:16:53.645 --> 00:16:54.733
But because of you,

00:16:54.734 --> 00:16:57.660
I also crumbled many times
in the prison you created.

00:17:00.545 --> 00:17:01.545
Prison?

00:17:07.048 --> 00:17:07.845
Yes.

00:17:08.575 --> 00:17:11.220
I've been in a prison
I made for myself.

00:17:11.875 --> 00:17:13.660
But I didn't want to be there alone.

00:17:14.915 --> 00:17:17.220
So I trapped you in my time.

00:17:23.325 --> 00:17:24.154
Bia,

00:17:25.502 --> 00:17:28.860
I was so scared you'd leave me.

00:17:29.215 --> 00:17:30.540
You feel the same, right?

00:17:30.780 --> 00:17:34.092
We're people left alone, right?

00:17:36.025 --> 00:17:38.275
We're inseparable, aren't we?

00:17:53.401 --> 00:17:54.830
The watch you gave me,

00:17:55.585 --> 00:17:57.810
it used to mean the world to me.

00:17:58.925 --> 00:18:00.110
But now I know.

00:18:03.065 --> 00:18:04.760
It was tying me down.

00:18:10.261 --> 00:18:12.945
Without you,
I don't know why I should live.

00:18:12.970 --> 00:18:15.436
You have to find your
own reason to live.

00:18:17.075 --> 00:18:18.492
If we stay trapped in that day,

00:18:19.263 --> 00:18:20.978
we'll both be unhappy.

00:18:24.628 --> 00:18:25.669
Are you unhappy?

00:18:27.645 --> 00:18:29.012
Look at yourself now.

00:18:39.645 --> 00:18:42.759
Do you think I don't know
you talk to this woman every day?

00:18:42.778 --> 00:18:44.634
It's because of the book publishing...

00:18:44.653 --> 00:18:47.281
Stop, stop using the
book as an excuse, please!

00:18:47.300 --> 00:18:48.499
It's disgusting!

00:18:55.485 --> 00:18:57.204
Director Yun, it's not like that...

00:18:57.224 --> 00:18:57.901
Ouch!

00:18:59.665 --> 00:19:01.270
Hey, Sul Jaehee!

00:19:03.085 --> 00:19:05.072
You're amazing, Yun Bia.

00:19:05.073 --> 00:19:07.179
I know, Sul Jaehee.

00:19:14.645 --> 00:19:16.549
I've found my own time now.

00:19:17.903 --> 00:19:19.262
But you're still

00:19:19.879 --> 00:19:21.669
trapped in that day's time.

00:19:26.255 --> 00:19:27.224
Jaehee.

00:19:32.305 --> 00:19:33.591
Jaehee.

00:19:37.245 --> 00:19:39.300
You can't stay there forever.

00:19:42.195 --> 00:19:44.158
Just like you freed me,

00:19:46.083 --> 00:19:47.960
I'll free you now.

00:20:19.221 --> 00:20:21.075
Breaking news just in.

00:20:21.186 --> 00:20:24.983
The former co-Director
of 'It's You' Sul Jaehee,

00:20:25.017 --> 00:20:27.548
a key suspect in hit-and-run
case of late Yang Seonae,

00:20:27.567 --> 00:20:29.795
has turned herself in
to police today.

00:20:30.090 --> 00:20:31.810
The police are focusing on

00:20:31.811 --> 00:20:37.110
investigating the exact circumstances
of the incident and the escape route...

00:20:37.289 --> 00:20:40.189
[Yang Seonae
1968-2025]

00:20:40.387 --> 00:20:41.351
I hated...

00:20:42.991 --> 00:20:45.008
mom so much,

00:20:47.646 --> 00:20:49.790
that I believed I abandoned her.

00:20:51.020 --> 00:20:52.020
But...

00:20:56.461 --> 00:20:57.751
I actually...

00:20:59.501 --> 00:21:01.299
loved her so much.

00:21:02.725 --> 00:21:04.610
Because I couldn't abandon her,

00:21:06.575 --> 00:21:08.090
it was painful.

00:21:11.479 --> 00:21:12.990
Goodbye, Mom.

00:21:53.468 --> 00:21:55.542
What was the little paradise

00:21:56.605 --> 00:21:57.994
my mom talked about?

00:22:00.715 --> 00:22:02.110
It must have been love.

00:22:04.705 --> 00:22:07.054
Even though I was the older brother,
unlike Baekho,

00:22:07.679 --> 00:22:09.193
I wasn't brave.

00:22:10.675 --> 00:22:14.621
After my mom passed away,
I hid in my own world.

00:22:15.746 --> 00:22:18.385
Aunt Seonae brought
me out into the world.

00:22:19.135 --> 00:22:21.987
How did she manage to
come out into the real world?

00:22:24.335 --> 00:22:25.725
I was always curious about that.

00:22:26.780 --> 00:22:29.165
When Aunt Seonae talked about someone,

00:22:29.480 --> 00:22:32.375
she shone like
the happiest person in the world.

00:22:33.950 --> 00:22:35.435
She said,

00:22:36.130 --> 00:22:37.778
when I fall in love
with someone,

00:22:38.017 --> 00:22:40.036
I'll be able to
write a real novel.

00:22:42.479 --> 00:22:44.768
Hidden within the darkness she fled
from, wanting so desperately to escape,

00:22:44.904 --> 00:22:47.500
was the paradise she
dreamed of all along.

00:22:50.475 --> 00:22:52.521
A very small but happy

00:22:55.348 --> 00:22:57.033
paradise of her own.

00:23:00.835 --> 00:23:02.270
Who was it?

00:23:07.124 --> 00:23:10.421
[Co-Director Yun Bia's
Emergency Press Conference]

00:23:20.818 --> 00:23:23.266
Before we begin the announcement,

00:23:23.286 --> 00:23:26.316
we apologize to the shareholders and users

00:23:26.943 --> 00:23:28.118
affected by this incident.

00:23:29.788 --> 00:23:33.837
- I take full responsibility...
- Yun Bia, what are your future plans?

00:23:33.857 --> 00:23:35.099
What will happen to 'It's You'?

00:23:35.119 --> 00:23:36.600
Are you staying with the company?

00:23:36.620 --> 00:23:39.112
- Are you completely losing your position?
- Who's taking over the company?

00:23:39.132 --> 00:23:41.169
What happens to Han Sunho and 'It's You'?

00:23:56.902 --> 00:23:59.754
Han Sunho just posted
something on social media.

00:23:59.755 --> 00:24:00.846
What's it about?

00:24:01.071 --> 00:24:02.616
Han Sunho is announcing a new work.

00:24:02.841 --> 00:24:03.946
What's the title?

00:24:04.101 --> 00:24:05.316
Love Phobia?

00:24:05.336 --> 00:24:06.336
Phobia?

00:24:06.458 --> 00:24:08.666
So, is it like a fear or something?

00:24:10.194 --> 00:24:11.345
Love.

00:24:12.667 --> 00:24:13.667
Pho.

00:24:15.082 --> 00:24:16.214
Bia?

00:24:18.368 --> 00:24:19.643
A new work?

00:24:24.018 --> 00:24:25.732
Han Sunho, what's this about?

00:24:25.751 --> 00:24:26.977
Without even a word to me.

00:24:27.956 --> 00:24:30.747
More importantly,
is it okay to announce it now?

00:24:30.767 --> 00:24:33.002
It's just going to stir up
more public opinion.

00:24:35.266 --> 00:24:38.402
I learned from Director Yun to
use public opinion to our advantage.

00:24:38.462 --> 00:24:41.520
Redirecting the arrows
meant for Bia to me.

00:24:42.495 --> 00:24:43.464
And

00:24:43.483 --> 00:24:45.829
I want people to know now.

00:24:46.977 --> 00:24:50.375
What kind of heart Bia had
when creating 'It's You'.

00:24:50.600 --> 00:24:52.235
Still, though.

00:24:52.630 --> 00:24:54.431
Did you even write anything?

00:24:54.450 --> 00:24:55.975
If you did, at least let me...

00:25:11.962 --> 00:25:15.232
We've all been deeply hurt
by the ones we love the most,

00:25:16.505 --> 00:25:17.801
Right?

00:25:19.435 --> 00:25:20.850
I have too.

00:25:22.035 --> 00:25:24.821
Love is uncertain and unpredictable.

00:25:25.490 --> 00:25:26.723
I foolishly thought

00:25:27.375 --> 00:25:29.062
it was a disease

00:25:29.552 --> 00:25:31.335
that would last forever.

00:25:32.455 --> 00:25:33.547
So I

00:25:34.472 --> 00:25:36.670
created my own little world

00:25:37.193 --> 00:25:38.810
and hid inside it.

00:25:39.985 --> 00:25:40.972
But

00:25:41.560 --> 00:25:42.812
ironically,

00:25:44.179 --> 00:25:47.558
even though I believed nothing could
remain unchanged,

00:25:47.964 --> 00:25:51.330
I hoped something would.

00:25:53.485 --> 00:25:58.008
'It's You' isn't just a mere
escape and a small world.

00:25:58.833 --> 00:26:00.527
It's also a world for someone,

00:26:01.623 --> 00:26:03.814
who hasn't given up on love.

00:26:08.567 --> 00:26:10.202
And I realized.

00:26:11.865 --> 00:26:14.561
Uncertain and
unpredictable changes

00:26:15.764 --> 00:26:17.327
are also part of love.

00:26:19.065 --> 00:26:20.685
The same goes for 'It's You'.

00:26:20.705 --> 00:26:25.231
I can't clearly say
what form it will change into yet.

00:26:25.815 --> 00:26:28.720
But I can assure you.

00:26:29.215 --> 00:26:34.344
'It's You' will not hide or retreat
and will continue to develop positively

00:26:34.605 --> 00:26:37.980
to take responsibility in any situation.

00:26:39.325 --> 00:26:41.298
I promise you all.

00:26:52.004 --> 00:26:53.728
Oh? Han Sunho!

00:26:56.507 --> 00:26:58.949
When is Han Sunho's new work
being released?

00:26:58.969 --> 00:27:01.064
What does Love Phobia mean?

00:27:01.084 --> 00:27:02.599
Can you say something about the new work?

00:27:02.619 --> 00:27:03.818
Is the new work a romance?

00:27:03.943 --> 00:27:06.148
What's your relationship with each other?

00:27:17.032 --> 00:27:19.449
Hey, did you see Han Sunho's social media?

00:27:19.715 --> 00:27:21.205
Finally, Han Sunho's new work is
coming out.

00:27:21.218 --> 00:27:23.313
'It's You' is all the rage these days.

00:27:23.335 --> 00:27:25.460
Yeah, it's even popping up
in the algorithm.

00:27:25.515 --> 00:27:29.876
The Director I know
would never do that.

00:27:29.896 --> 00:27:30.771
Gosh.

00:27:30.835 --> 00:27:32.295
I knew this would happen.

00:27:32.322 --> 00:27:35.464
They didn't create 'It's You'
with bad intentions from the start.

00:27:35.465 --> 00:27:36.277
Our elders...

00:27:36.278 --> 00:27:38.559
Director doesn't
seem like a bad person.

00:27:38.578 --> 00:27:40.349
There must be a reason.

00:27:40.350 --> 00:27:41.350
Exactly.

00:27:42.440 --> 00:27:43.440
Wow.

00:27:43.580 --> 00:27:44.730
I'm really relieved.

00:27:44.741 --> 00:27:45.549
We almost had a big
problem on our hands.

00:27:45.569 --> 00:27:47.205
I almost became jobless at my age.

00:27:48.400 --> 00:27:51.568
But how did you come up
with that idea, Yukyung?

00:27:52.285 --> 00:27:54.136
It's a piece of cake.

00:27:54.155 --> 00:27:57.735
I just added a spoonful of interview to
the good deed Director Yun did.

00:27:57.760 --> 00:27:58.815
Impressive.

00:27:59.199 --> 00:28:00.869
Cheers to that?

00:28:01.021 --> 00:28:02.296
- Cheers!
- Cheers!

00:28:03.135 --> 00:28:04.494
This should've been real booze.

00:28:04.495 --> 00:28:05.375
- Right.
- Right.

00:28:05.395 --> 00:28:06.640
Even if it were beer.

00:28:57.208 --> 00:28:59.488
It's been a while.

00:28:59.939 --> 00:29:00.650
Yeah.

00:29:01.645 --> 00:29:03.134
It's been a while, Mom.

00:29:04.381 --> 00:29:05.409
Really.

00:29:06.515 --> 00:29:08.318
How have you been?

00:29:10.105 --> 00:29:11.127
I've been...

00:29:12.481 --> 00:29:14.570
having a very long dream.

00:29:15.548 --> 00:29:18.155
A dream that wouldn't end for a long time.

00:29:18.807 --> 00:29:20.153
I thought...

00:29:21.603 --> 00:29:23.700
I'd live in that dream forever.

00:29:25.712 --> 00:29:27.027
But not anymore.

00:29:28.055 --> 00:29:30.210
Was it Han Sunho

00:29:31.286 --> 00:29:32.849
who woke you from that dream?

00:29:33.855 --> 00:29:35.420
How did you know?

00:29:35.750 --> 00:29:39.135
I told you,
Han Sunho is your destined one.

00:29:41.385 --> 00:29:43.557
Right, you did say that.

00:29:45.322 --> 00:29:46.442
But I...

00:29:47.429 --> 00:29:49.386
don't think it's destiny.

00:29:49.768 --> 00:29:50.707
Then what?

00:29:51.237 --> 00:29:53.073
If it weren't for him,

00:29:53.303 --> 00:29:56.133
I might never have come
out into the world.

00:29:57.495 --> 00:29:58.582
But.

00:30:00.107 --> 00:30:02.580
I believe it was ultimately my choice.

00:30:05.396 --> 00:30:07.380
You have grown up a lot.

00:30:08.611 --> 00:30:09.611
So,

00:30:10.193 --> 00:30:11.498
I'm going to...

00:30:12.874 --> 00:30:14.410
leave the dream

00:30:16.075 --> 00:30:17.480
and live in reality.

00:30:27.808 --> 00:30:29.043
I'm sorry, Mom.

00:30:34.641 --> 00:30:35.641
And

00:30:38.203 --> 00:30:39.516
thank you.

00:30:46.721 --> 00:30:47.721
'ForMe'.

00:30:49.864 --> 00:30:51.474
Yang Seonae's program.

00:30:56.996 --> 00:30:58.170
Delete.

00:31:00.788 --> 00:31:02.596
I love you, Bia.

00:31:25.734 --> 00:31:27.337
It's really ending now.

00:31:28.355 --> 00:31:30.664
It's because I can
finally see the end,

00:31:31.173 --> 00:31:32.350
it feels strange.

00:31:33.045 --> 00:31:34.397
I feel calm.

00:31:35.545 --> 00:31:36.546
Actually,

00:31:37.204 --> 00:31:38.928
there was a cold corner
in my heart before,

00:31:39.562 --> 00:31:43.693
so I didn't realize
how beautiful those lights were.

00:31:45.934 --> 00:31:47.410
Has it changed now?

00:31:49.705 --> 00:31:51.027
Thanks to someone,

00:31:52.207 --> 00:31:54.381
I realized even the darkness

00:31:54.470 --> 00:31:55.730
can be this pretty.

00:32:01.124 --> 00:32:04.395
But what's that in your bag?

00:32:04.595 --> 00:32:05.595
Right.

00:32:07.078 --> 00:32:08.080
Ta-da!

00:32:10.275 --> 00:32:12.176
You've been carrying this around?

00:32:12.196 --> 00:32:13.483
Don't you carry this?

00:32:13.503 --> 00:32:14.257
Hm?

00:32:14.745 --> 00:32:15.306
Well...

00:32:15.325 --> 00:32:16.568
I'm a bit disappointed.

00:32:16.793 --> 00:32:18.060
You didn't throw away the toy, did you?

00:32:19.125 --> 00:32:22.040
Throw it away?
No way, it's safely at home.

00:32:22.905 --> 00:32:24.170
I don't believe that.

00:32:24.195 --> 00:32:26.230
Then come to my home
and check for yourself.

00:32:27.038 --> 00:32:28.243
That's refreshing.

00:32:29.125 --> 00:32:30.385
What is?

00:32:31.110 --> 00:32:33.645
It's like another version
of "Wanna come over for ramyeon?"

00:32:34.995 --> 00:32:36.560
You must be crazy!

00:32:38.206 --> 00:32:39.850
Where are you going?

00:32:50.440 --> 00:32:53.102
[One Year Later]

00:32:58.535 --> 00:33:00.397
Oh? You're up?

00:33:02.295 --> 00:33:03.690
What's all this?

00:33:04.515 --> 00:33:06.400
I tried making some breakfast.

00:33:22.715 --> 00:33:23.743
How does it taste?

00:33:29.475 --> 00:33:30.690
Han Sunho.

00:33:30.815 --> 00:33:31.815
This is good, right?

00:33:32.370 --> 00:33:34.665
You should stick to writing, not cooking.

00:33:38.073 --> 00:33:39.425
That can't be true.

00:33:39.750 --> 00:33:41.345
Go ahead, try it.

00:33:44.180 --> 00:33:45.225
Doesn't it taste weird?

00:33:45.390 --> 00:33:46.490
Tastes fine to me.

00:33:46.818 --> 00:33:47.818
What?

00:33:48.115 --> 00:33:49.350
You're just saying that.

00:33:49.370 --> 00:33:50.445
Try the other stuff too.

00:33:50.465 --> 00:33:55.460
Why should I trust the other stuff?

00:33:56.115 --> 00:33:57.600
You try it first.

00:33:57.902 --> 00:34:00.127
Just watching you eat fills me up.

00:34:00.383 --> 00:34:02.465
[Boramgadeuk Dementia Center]

00:34:06.782 --> 00:34:10.400
[Innovative approaches to dementia
treatment via AI mixed-reality technology]

00:34:16.627 --> 00:34:17.774
Hello.

00:34:18.085 --> 00:34:20.550
I'm Yun Bia,
a temporary employee at 'It's You'.

00:34:20.945 --> 00:34:24.310
Thank you for taking the time to be here.

00:34:38.470 --> 00:34:40.790
Originally, 'It's You' aimed to

00:34:40.872 --> 00:34:44.269
alleviate people's loneliness
through AI technology

00:34:44.311 --> 00:34:48.457
and provide mental and emotional care.

00:34:48.790 --> 00:34:50.968
To revive this original value,

00:34:50.988 --> 00:34:54.595
we're repurposing It's You's
accumulated AI mixed reality technology

00:34:54.666 --> 00:34:57.014
for dementia patient support,
senior welfare,

00:34:57.015 --> 00:35:01.210
and mental health management programs.

00:35:02.428 --> 00:35:06.700
How will the dementia-specific
program be offered?

00:35:06.925 --> 00:35:11.587
Through mixed reality content,
dementia patients can relive memories

00:35:11.607 --> 00:35:14.743
or safely receive cognitive training.

00:35:15.075 --> 00:35:17.273
And it's free.

00:35:17.878 --> 00:35:19.900
Oh my, free cognitive training?

00:35:23.206 --> 00:35:25.508
I'm taking responsibility

00:35:25.701 --> 00:35:29.244
and handling the issues to the end.

00:35:29.735 --> 00:35:35.088
I want to show that AI can be
a positive technology

00:35:35.147 --> 00:35:39.348
that helps the socially
vulnerable and heals wounds.

00:35:39.455 --> 00:35:42.331
Thank you for listening to
the presentation.

00:36:14.421 --> 00:36:15.700
Yes, of course.

00:36:15.701 --> 00:36:19.672
Now that Han Sunho has started,
his next work will come out soon.

00:36:19.691 --> 00:36:21.536
Yes, hold on a moment.

00:36:23.804 --> 00:36:24.614
Yes.

00:36:25.625 --> 00:36:27.410
An interview with Han Sunho?

00:36:27.430 --> 00:36:28.660
Of course.

00:36:28.805 --> 00:36:30.870
Han Sunho lives off his looks...

00:36:36.207 --> 00:36:37.166
Ah.

00:36:37.185 --> 00:36:38.220
No, no.

00:36:38.455 --> 00:36:39.580
Hold on.

00:36:41.475 --> 00:36:43.960
You'll do the interview, right?

00:36:44.615 --> 00:36:45.720
Hey?

00:36:48.894 --> 00:36:52.550
He is busy writing...

00:36:52.985 --> 00:36:54.990
Yes, just a moment.

00:36:56.765 --> 00:36:57.870
Hello?

00:36:59.325 --> 00:37:01.560
How have you been, Jiyoung?

00:37:01.980 --> 00:37:02.980
Yes.

00:37:03.828 --> 00:37:05.208
Me too.

00:37:06.629 --> 00:37:08.478
[Bia]

00:37:12.489 --> 00:37:13.536
[Bia]

00:37:16.125 --> 00:37:17.286
Did the presentation go well?

00:37:17.379 --> 00:37:18.674
Just finished.

00:37:18.829 --> 00:37:21.074
How's the book writing going?

00:37:21.870 --> 00:37:23.605
I'm stuck on a part.

00:37:24.212 --> 00:37:27.107
The male lead fell asleep at
the female lead's house,

00:37:27.420 --> 00:37:30.005
and she doodled on
his face while he slept.

00:37:30.080 --> 00:37:31.685
When he woke up,

00:37:31.875 --> 00:37:33.576
she was wiping his face

00:37:34.143 --> 00:37:35.510
and then kissed him.

00:37:35.825 --> 00:37:38.070
What do you think
the female lead was feeling then?

00:37:38.535 --> 00:37:39.321
I...

00:37:39.568 --> 00:37:40.917
I don't know?

00:37:41.365 --> 00:37:44.630
Isn't that something
the writer should imagine?

00:37:44.696 --> 00:37:46.709
Well... I... Um...

00:37:46.991 --> 00:37:47.991
I'll hang up now.

00:37:56.220 --> 00:37:59.590
I gave a presentation for
an hour and a half.

00:38:01.344 --> 00:38:05.207
An hour and a half.

00:38:14.464 --> 00:38:19.996
[Free ForMe AI Service]

00:38:23.367 --> 00:38:26.381
Our company has many complaints
after the restructuring,

00:38:26.382 --> 00:38:28.847
but it's much more rewarding
than before, right?

00:38:28.872 --> 00:38:29.872
Exactly.

00:38:30.282 --> 00:38:32.647
Director Yun is really amazing.

00:38:32.702 --> 00:38:37.047
Since transitioning to a public service,
we're getting a lot of public funding.

00:38:37.311 --> 00:38:39.502
And isn't it a bit less tiring?

00:38:39.522 --> 00:38:41.277
Thinking about all the overtime before...

00:38:41.298 --> 00:38:42.238
Gosh...

00:38:42.374 --> 00:38:43.397
Right.

00:38:44.065 --> 00:38:45.855
I've never done overtime, though.

00:38:50.697 --> 00:38:53.284
Habitual overtime is unproductive.

00:38:54.090 --> 00:38:55.616
Jooyeon!

00:38:55.859 --> 00:38:56.587
Wow!

00:38:56.647 --> 00:38:58.379
How long has it been?

00:38:58.504 --> 00:38:59.464
How have you been?

00:38:59.464 --> 00:39:00.139
Good.

00:39:00.140 --> 00:39:01.810
How does it feel to be back at work?

00:39:03.235 --> 00:39:05.059
Did you miss me a bit while I was gone?

00:39:05.084 --> 00:39:05.922
Of course.

00:39:06.995 --> 00:39:08.314
No way!

00:39:08.361 --> 00:39:09.404
What happened?

00:39:09.523 --> 00:39:10.523
What do we do about this?

00:39:11.285 --> 00:39:12.370
What's up with Yukyung?

00:39:14.125 --> 00:39:16.850
Jooyeon, let's catch up later.

00:39:19.373 --> 00:39:20.525
Where's she going?

00:39:20.550 --> 00:39:21.390
I wonder.

00:39:21.700 --> 00:39:22.855
Thank you.

00:39:23.014 --> 00:39:25.488
[Book Signing Event]

00:39:25.602 --> 00:39:27.103
[Writer Han Sunho's Book Signing]

00:39:27.210 --> 00:39:28.435
What's your name?

00:39:32.493 --> 00:39:34.090
Hello, Mr. Han.

00:39:35.095 --> 00:39:36.016
What's your name?

00:39:36.035 --> 00:39:37.430
I'm Yusol.

00:39:42.445 --> 00:39:43.440
Thank you.

00:39:43.460 --> 00:39:44.529
Thank you.

00:39:44.719 --> 00:39:45.412
What's your name?

00:39:45.413 --> 00:39:46.489
I'm Yeju.

00:39:47.214 --> 00:39:49.990
I really love your book.

00:39:51.215 --> 00:39:52.155
Thanks.

00:39:52.156 --> 00:39:55.580
Isn't the protagonist in your book
based on the 'It's You' incident?

00:39:56.343 --> 00:39:59.155
Let's just say it's inspired by
their love and growth.

00:40:00.680 --> 00:40:02.200
- Thank you.
- Thank you.

00:40:03.208 --> 00:40:04.208
Next, please.

00:40:12.382 --> 00:40:13.382
Next, please.

00:40:16.501 --> 00:40:19.762
You're having a book signing
and didn't even tell me?

00:40:20.499 --> 00:40:21.484
Really?

00:40:21.580 --> 00:40:23.359
It's not that I didn't want to tell you,

00:40:23.795 --> 00:40:26.330
but you've been busy
with the company renewal.

00:40:26.555 --> 00:40:27.317
So,

00:40:27.860 --> 00:40:30.575
are you upset because I
haven't been meeting you lately?

00:40:30.900 --> 00:40:32.038
Well...

00:40:32.163 --> 00:40:35.124
You've been distant with Sunho too,
so why bother?

00:40:36.535 --> 00:40:37.535
Jealous?

00:40:37.746 --> 00:40:39.044
Jealous? No way

00:40:39.045 --> 00:40:41.885
I'm busy too, you know, not just you.

00:40:42.835 --> 00:40:43.835
Right.

00:40:43.965 --> 00:40:46.310
We're both busy, so why keep in touch?

00:40:46.465 --> 00:40:48.010
Let's just live our own lives.

00:40:48.045 --> 00:40:49.810
It's not like we're dating or anything.

00:40:51.166 --> 00:40:53.655
Wait, why aren't we dating?

00:40:54.480 --> 00:40:56.155
Since when were we dating?

00:40:56.980 --> 00:40:58.844
Yukyung, don't get mad...

00:40:58.845 --> 00:41:00.750
Why are you acting like this?

00:41:00.775 --> 00:41:02.490
What do you mean, acting?

00:41:03.085 --> 00:41:04.085
Then

00:41:05.099 --> 00:41:08.230
let's start dating from today!

00:41:26.153 --> 00:41:28.090
Are you two finally dating?

00:41:28.644 --> 00:41:31.390
That's great!

00:41:31.627 --> 00:41:32.819
Jiyoung.

00:41:32.844 --> 00:41:34.210
How have you been?

00:41:34.230 --> 00:41:35.615
Congrats to you both.

00:41:35.840 --> 00:41:36.970
Applause!

00:41:42.702 --> 00:41:44.024
You two look great together!

00:41:46.698 --> 00:41:48.131
[Love Phobia]

00:41:49.358 --> 00:41:50.980
Oh? Sorry.

00:41:52.155 --> 00:41:53.155
What's your name?

00:41:53.965 --> 00:41:55.171
I'm Yun Bia.

00:41:59.581 --> 00:42:00.841
Bia, when did you get here?

00:42:00.889 --> 00:42:03.195
For Mr. Han's fan signing...

00:42:05.453 --> 00:42:06.766
Of course,

00:42:06.829 --> 00:42:08.334
I had to come to
the book signing.

00:42:08.850 --> 00:42:10.470
Hurry and sign for me.

00:42:20.731 --> 00:42:21.956
Congrats.

00:42:22.195 --> 00:42:23.224
Thanks.

00:42:31.292 --> 00:42:32.922
Cheers!

00:42:34.147 --> 00:42:35.391
It's been a while, everyone.

00:42:42.244 --> 00:42:43.635
Jiyoung, it's been so long!

00:42:43.636 --> 00:42:44.636
I know, right?

00:42:50.506 --> 00:42:51.506
Oh!

00:42:51.648 --> 00:42:53.707
Everyone, listen up!

00:42:55.615 --> 00:42:56.615
Jiyoung.

00:42:57.627 --> 00:42:58.720
Bring it out quickly.

00:42:59.705 --> 00:43:01.304
I'm embarrassed.

00:43:01.329 --> 00:43:02.551
Hurry up.

00:43:03.539 --> 00:43:04.631
What's that?

00:43:08.247 --> 00:43:10.590
Everyone, my book is out.

00:43:11.156 --> 00:43:12.156
Really?

00:43:12.485 --> 00:43:13.870
Wow, can I see it?

00:43:14.685 --> 00:43:16.970
Let's clap first!

00:43:17.511 --> 00:43:20.596
Thank you, thank you, thank you.

00:43:21.063 --> 00:43:21.784
Here!

00:43:21.837 --> 00:43:23.710
Please promote my book a lot.

00:43:23.845 --> 00:43:25.730
Spread the word about my book.

00:43:26.235 --> 00:43:27.783
- Here you go.
- I'll read it well.

00:43:27.803 --> 00:43:29.576
Enjoy reading my book.

00:43:29.632 --> 00:43:30.666
Thank you.

00:43:30.686 --> 00:43:32.735
This doesn't look like you.

00:43:32.755 --> 00:43:34.798
That's totally me, what are you saying?

00:43:39.316 --> 00:43:41.063
It's really almost over now.

00:43:42.035 --> 00:43:45.410
Bia, your new time starts now.

00:43:47.325 --> 00:43:48.470
Where should we go?

00:43:50.061 --> 00:43:52.206
Let's go anywhere!

00:43:59.582 --> 00:44:01.197
The moon is so big.

00:44:03.545 --> 00:44:05.388
What you wanted most

00:44:05.713 --> 00:44:07.453
was to work normally,

00:44:07.578 --> 00:44:08.578
have company dinners,

00:44:09.000 --> 00:44:10.418
and choose lunch menus.

00:44:11.422 --> 00:44:12.508
Is that it?

00:44:13.805 --> 00:44:15.210
I'm doing that right now.

00:44:17.314 --> 00:44:18.314
Then...

00:44:18.654 --> 00:44:20.563
want to add one more ordinary thing?

00:44:21.415 --> 00:44:22.415
What's that?

00:44:22.520 --> 00:44:25.210
Something everyone does,
something very ordinary.

00:44:43.890 --> 00:44:45.700
Do you know why a ring is called a ring?

00:44:47.235 --> 00:44:49.860
Because it's half of a pair, they say.

00:44:50.955 --> 00:44:52.280
Two become one.

00:45:04.581 --> 00:45:05.695
I'll always...

00:45:06.411 --> 00:45:08.110
be by your side, Bia.

00:45:11.774 --> 00:45:13.600
This is what it felt like.

00:45:14.615 --> 00:45:15.615
What did?

00:45:16.844 --> 00:45:19.645
The feeling the
female protagonist had

00:45:19.861 --> 00:45:23.705
when she kissed the
hero in your novel.

00:45:28.786 --> 00:45:30.340
The feeling of love.

00:45:44.160 --> 00:45:46.555
Love is about not getting hurt

00:45:46.654 --> 00:45:49.293
and being satisfied with each other,
only showing the good sides.

00:45:49.313 --> 00:45:50.313
Good morning!

00:45:52.221 --> 00:45:53.195
Thank you.

00:45:53.215 --> 00:45:55.401
I thought unchanging love

00:45:55.420 --> 00:45:58.108
was the most ideal thing.

00:45:59.333 --> 00:46:00.440
But it wasn't.

00:46:00.596 --> 00:46:02.096
[Writer Song Jiyoung Book Signing Event]

00:46:02.233 --> 00:46:03.668
Now I know.

00:46:04.105 --> 00:46:05.665
Even if we're different

00:46:05.941 --> 00:46:08.498
and show our weaknesses
and shortcomings,

00:46:10.266 --> 00:46:12.971
and even if we change someday,

00:46:15.021 --> 00:46:17.081
wanting to be together in this moment,

00:46:17.706 --> 00:46:21.860
that courage is what true love is.